{"title":"新儿歌","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":5,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"新儿歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红公鸡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红公鸡，绿尾巴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早起唱歌催大家："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“喔、喔、喔、起来吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喔、喔、喔，起来吧！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爸爸挑担上圩堤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈上山采油茶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哥嫂双双挖河泥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我带妹妹蹲在家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想到一个好办法；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"门口挖团黄泥巴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做它一个胖娃娃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妹妹一见咧嘴笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不哭不闹不喊妈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻轻悄悄溜出门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"找个粪筐和粪扒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屋前屋后拾野粪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送到社里垩庄稼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主任、社员都欢喜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夸我是个好娃娃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（江苏溧水）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小毛驴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小毛驴，撅尾巴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺爷牵它上北洼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钉上四只铁蹄子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"入到庄里顶呱呱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男女庄员都称赞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爷爷听了笑掉牙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（河南）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小星星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小星星，亮晶晶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照得村庄家家明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是天上有星星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是咱社里装电灯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（福建）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全家老少起五更"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大哥驮犁出了门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二哥牵牛后面跟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嫂嫂下厨烧着锅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姐姐端起猪食盆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我从床上爬起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东方没亮还有星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都为春耕大生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全家老少起五更。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（安徽）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日子过得像朵花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合作化，好处大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的家，变样啦！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爹娘不顶嘴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兄嫂不吵架；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我爱妹妹年龄小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弟弟尊我比他大。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全家同心忙生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日子过得像朵花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（福建）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小水库"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小水库，圆又圆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"栽藕种菱又养鲢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过中秋，过大年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有荤有素又卖钱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小水库，圆又圆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"方圆尽是社里田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"稻子壮，穗穗结，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水库像个青荷叶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小水库，圆又圆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"方圆尽是社里田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"稻子黄，金闪闪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰收人人都喜欢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（安徽）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"除四害"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小扫帚，沉甸甸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奶奶扫地把腰弯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扫罢厨房扫住室，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"街院厕所都扫遍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一星灰尘都不粘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（河南巩县）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼科小专家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小小扇子两面花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是眼科小专家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈叫，嫂嫂请，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫我治他们的睁眼瞎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不用诊脉不吃药，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开个单方“学文化”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈笑，嫂嫂夸："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“这个医生真不差"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啥时治好俺的病，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做件新衣送给他”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（河南）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月亮走我也走"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月亮走，我也走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我给月亮背笆篓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一背背到大桥头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轮船桥下过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行人桥上走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火车汽车江上跑；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龟山蛇山牵上手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（湖北武汉）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}